<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Ketivee</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="assets/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <meta name="description" content="Ketivee Privacy Policy">

</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Ketivee Privacy Policy</h1>
        <button id="menu-toggle" title="Toggle Menu">☰</button>
    </header>
    <button id="theme-toggle" title="Toggle Theme">🌒</button>

    <!-- Side Menu -->
    <aside class="hidden">
        <h3>Sections</h3>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
            <li><a href="#policy-intro">Introduction</a></li>
            <li><a href="#data-security">Data Security</a></li>
            <li><a href="#donated-data">Donated Data</a></li>
            <li><a href="#data-usage">Data Usage</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact-us">Contact Us</a></li>
        </ul>
    </aside>
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main style="flex: 1; padding: 20px;">
        <section id="policy-intro">
            <h3>Introduction</h3>
            <p>
                We value your trust at Ketivee. We want to assure you that your data is safe, secure, and handled with
                the utmost transparency. We strictly adhere to ethical data practices, and our Privacy Policy is
                designed to ensure that your data is always protected.
            </p>
        </section>
        <hr>

        <section id="data-security">
            <h3>Data Security</h3>
            <p>
                Ketivee is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your data. We do not sell
                or share any data with third parties. All data donated to us is encrypted and stored securely, ensuring
                complete safety. Ketivee does not read or access your personal data without your explicit permission. We
                understand that privacy is important to you, and we are committed to safeguarding it..
            </p>
        </section>
        <hr>

        <section id="donated-data">
            <h3>Donated Data</h3>
            <p>Any data donated to us for the SarthiAI project is used solely for improving our AI models. We are
                committed to maintaining your privacy while advancing our technology for the benefit of everyone. This
                commitment means that we will never share your personal data with any third party, including advertisers
                and analytics providers. We will also never use your personal data to train or develop our AI models.
                Instead, we will use anonymized and aggregated data to train our models and develop new AI applications.
                Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. By donating your data to the
                SarthiAI project, you are helping us to develop AI applications that can improve the lives of everyone.
            </p>
        </section>
        <hr>

        <section id="data-usage">
            <h3>Data Usage</h3>
            <p>
                Your privacy matter for us, At Ketivee, your data is yours—always. We never use your information for advertising or marketing
                purposes. Transparency is at the core of everything we do, with all our processes being open and
                accessible.

                If you have any questions about how we handle your data, please reach out. We're here to ensure you have
                full control and confidence in your experience with us.
            </p>
        </section>
        <hr>

        <section id="contact-us">
            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <p>
                For any concerns or questions, you can contact us at:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@ketivee.com">support@ketivee.com</a></li>
                <li>Website: <a href="https://ketivee.com">https://ketivee.com</a></li>
                <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/ketivee-org">https://github.com/ketivee-org</a></li>
            </ul>
            <img src="../assets/images/contact_us.svg" alt="Contact Us" class="ai-image">
            <a href="https://donation.ketivee.com"><button>Take me back</button> </a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 Ketivee | <a href="https://github.com/ketivee-org">GitHub</a> | Empowering Creators with AI
    </footer>

    <script>
        const themeToggle = document.getElementById('theme-toggle');
        const body = document.body;


        // Set default theme to dark
        body.classList.add('dark-mode');
        themeToggle.textContent = '☀️';

        // Theme Toggle Functionality
        themeToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const isDarkMode = body.classList.toggle('dark-mode');
            themeToggle.textContent = isDarkMode ? '☀️' : '🌒';
        });

        // Smooth Scrolling for Side Menu Links
        document.querySelectorAll("aside ul li a").forEach((link) => {
            link.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                const targetId = link.getAttribute("href").substring(1);
                const targetElement = document.getElementById(targetId);
                targetElement.scrollIntoView({ behavior: "smooth" });
            });

            // Toggle Side Menu
            const menuToggle = document.getElementById("menu-toggle");
            const sideMenu = document.querySelector("aside");

            menuToggle.addEventListener("click", () => {
                sideMenu.classList.toggle("shown");
                sideMenu.classList.toggle("hidden");
            });

        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>